-Can you please sign this?
-my first love again?

13
00:01:49,484 --> 00:01:52,529
I don't intend to date anyone for a while,
and I don't have time for it either.

14
00:01:53,196 --> 00:01:54,989
I'm telling you not to waste your time.

15
00:01:55,657 --> 00:01:56,950
I hope you quickly recover.

16
00:01:59,244 --> 00:02:00,954
He got the wrong idea though.

17
00:02:02,372 --> 00:02:05,250
For me, it wasn't love yet.

18
00:02:05,834 --> 00:02:07,794
That's for the cows.

19
00:02:10,797 --> 00:02:12,465
This is for us.

20
00:02:13,967 --> 00:02:15,009
Although...

21
00:02:16,386 --> 00:02:19,264
I was smitten with him for a little while
when I was a kid.

22
00:02:20,890 --> 00:02:21,766
"Lee Kang"?

23
00:02:22,809 --> 00:02:23,643
"Lee Kang"?

24
00:02:24,894 --> 00:02:27,355
-Do you know me?
-I didn't even remember his name

25
00:02:27,438 --> 00:02:31,317
because I had forgotten about him
for many years, and I thought

26
00:02:31,818 --> 00:02:34,404
I could quickly forget him
as soon as I left the hospital.

27
00:02:39,367 --> 00:02:40,493
Hey, hold on.

28
00:02:42,912 --> 00:02:45,623
Look at this.
It's spring water from Mount Gyeryong.

29
00:02:45,707 --> 00:02:49,127
We have to sprinkle this in all directions
to never be hospitalized again.

30
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:51,880
Hey, are you still going to
that male shaman?

31
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:55,717
Your talk about water
made me want to pee again.

32
00:02:56,509 --> 00:02:57,719
I'll be quick.

33
00:02:59,053 --> 00:03:00,054
Why you little...

34
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:03,600
You're supposed to be farting,
not pee like this again and again.

35
00:03:06,769 --> 00:03:08,229
Do better if you're embarrassed.

36
00:03:09,522 --> 00:03:10,857
What the hell did you say?

37
00:03:11,482 --> 00:03:12,942
You evil bastard.

38
00:03:13,443 --> 00:03:14,777
